<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Workflow on 晴耕雨讀</title><link>http://0x3f.org/tags/workflow/</link><description>Recent content in Workflow on 晴耕雨讀</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-cn</language><copyright>© 淘气 2022</copyright><lastBuildDate>Fri, 24 Mar 2017 21:09:13 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="http://0x3f.org/tags/workflow/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>自动探测RSS地址的workflow</title><link>http://0x3f.org/posts/find-rss-with-workflow/</link><pubDate>Fri, 24 Mar 2017 21:09:13 +0000</pubDate><guid>http://0x3f.org/posts/find-rss-with-workflow/</guid><description>&lt;p>RSS真是没落了，很多网站都没有明确输出Feed地址，每次想订阅都要浪费不少时间，所以写了这个&lt;a href="https://workflow.is/workflows/7f02a38a6c21414a96a4f96600c94662">Workflow&lt;/a>。&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>列出页面中所有的Feed地址，点击后复制到剪贴板&lt;/li>
&lt;li>如果页面中的Feed地址是相对地址，自动转换为绝对地址&lt;/li>
&lt;li>如果页面中没有Feed地址，列出常见的几种地址，并侦测被点选的地址，侦测成功后自动复制到剪贴板&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
